data.description: WOW!!! Price improvement plus the seller is offering a $5000 concession towards closing costs or rate buydown for all other financing! This home has an assumable VA loan at 3.375. Welcome to your new 3 bedroom/2 bathroom home with a full unfinished basement on 3.5 acres! The sellers have put over $40,000 in upgrades into this home including new flooring, new stainless-steel appliances, new paint, new lighting, new tankless water heater, a brand new HCAV system, a radon mitigation system, a Halo water purifying system that is made specifically for this home, the well was replaced a few years ago and the roof was replaced in 2022. The garage is oversized and has a new door as well. The home has all new flooring throughout and the rooms are spacious and inviting. The basement is a full unfinished basement that you can turn into whatever your heart desires! All that is left to do is for you to move in! Enjoy mornings and evenings on your back deck or front covered porch that faces the mountains. The property has a 12x24 horse shed with a pen and a separate pasture that is fenced for your horses. There is still plenty of room to add more horse pens or even an arena. Come take a look at this home, you will not be disappointed.
